HEADWORD: Scholarly
<hw>Schol"ar*ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Like a scholar, or learned
person; showing the qualities of a scholar; <as>as, a <ex>scholarly</ex>
essay or critique</as>.</def> -- <def2><pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a
scholarly manner.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
